      "post_content": "@Dib-Man  \n  \nEverything you said is correct except you can cast creatures in addition to instants and sorceries. In magic, cards are either Land or Spells. That's why card's like [Fork](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fork) have to clarify instant and sorcery spells. What this card is basically saying is that if you play a spell, skip your combat step. If you do combat, skip your main phases.",
      "posted_by": "SarpNasty",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost202379\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">@Dib-Man<br/><br/>Everything you said is correct except you can cast creatures in addition to instants and sorceries.  In magic, cards are either Land or Spells.   That's why card's like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fork\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fork\">Fork</a> have to clarify instant and sorcery spells.  What this card is basically saying is that if you play a spell, skip your combat step.  If you do combat, skip your main phases.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '202379'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy62590\">SarpNasty</span>\r\n                                (10/6/2011 6:38:09 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Sta